				<td colspan="2"><span>What level alts? Dont have to have perma rooted mobs in order to train weapon skills. I helped my rogue get some 1hb skill ups by holding aggro on some dulak boat mobs(Windscorn). Just sang SoS repeatedly with a primary hand lute. Never took much damage. Can always twist in Marr + Nivs if you need healing. The rogue beat on these mobs for a good 10-15 minutes before they'd start running and I'd kill them and grab another. Only took a couple hours to max it from skill 0(a lot of dext helps, IE kattas).
<br />

<br />
Some Windscorn boat mobs are lightblue at 65, Armory mobs in Dulak work well too.</span></td>
